channel.title: I need help setting my server up online
channel.description: My server Ive worked on has been nearly completed and I want to make it online so my friends and I can test it before making it worldwide. I followed a tutorial by mod harrison on youtube and I cannot get it to work. I have no-ip installed and running, along with bitTorrent so people can use it, and it doesnt work. I have the bitTorrent port thing as 43594. Can someone help me?
